sentences: Lars Ivar Edegran (born 1944) is a Dixieland jazz musician and bandleader from Sweden.
Edegran was born in Stockholm, Sweden and played in New Orleans style groups in Sweden before moving to New Orleans in 1966.
His theatrical arrangements include the music for the show One Mo' Time.
